{{Infobox Organization |name = Academy of Sciences of Moldova |image = Академия Наук Молдавии.jpg |image_border = |size = |alt = |caption = The building of the Academy of Science of Moldova in [[Chişinău]] |map = |msize = |malt = |mcaption = |abbreviation = |motto = |formation = 1946 |extinction = |type = |status = active |purpose = advocate and public voice, educator and network |headquarters = [[Chişinău]] |location = |region_served = |membership = |language = [[Romanian language]] |leader_title = President |leader_name = [[Gheorghe Duca (Academician)|Gheorghe Duca]] |main_organ = |parent_organization = |affiliations = |num_staff = |num_volunteers = |budget = |website = [http://www.asm.md/ official website] |remarks = }}
The '''Academy of Sciences of Moldova''' ({{lang-ro|Academia de Ştiinţe a Moldovei}}), established in 1946, is the main scientific organization of the [[Moldova|Republic of Moldova]] and coordinates research in all areas of science and technology.
== Presidents ==
[[Gheorghe Duca (Academician)|Gheorghe Duca]] has been the [[head of the Academy of Sciences of Moldova]] since February 5, 2004.
* [[Iachim Grosul]] (1961–1976) * [[Alexandru Jucenco]] (1977–1989) * [[Andrei Andrieş]] (1989&nbsp;– February 5, 2004) * [[Gheorghe Duca (Academician)|Gheorghe Duca]] (February 5, 2004&nbsp;– present)
==Decision of the Presidium of the Academy of Sciences of Moldova of September 9, 1994== "The annual general meeting of the Academy of Sciences of Moldova confirms the reasoned scientific opinion of philologists from the Republic and abroad (approved by the decision of the Presidium of Academy of Science of Moldova of 9.09.94), according to which the correct name of the State language (official) of the Republic of Moldova is Romanian. This declaration is to be given to advertising.
28.02.96 „Limba Română”, nr. 2 (26), 1996."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://limbaromana.md/index.php?go=articole&printversion=1&n=2482|title=Declaraţia Adunării Generale Anuale a Academiei de Ştiinţe a Moldovei - LimbaRomana|author=|date=|website=limbaromana.md|accessdate=14 April 2018}}</ref>
