'''Hostage Rescue Force''' (Arabic: قوة إنقاذ الرهائن ) is Egypt's premier domestic [[counter-terrorism]] and [[hostage]] rescue unit. It is subordinate to the National Security Directorate of the [[Ministry of Interior (Egypt)|Egyptian Ministry of Interior]].

