'''''La Nation''''' is the government-owned [[newspaper]] of [[Benin]]. It was renamed from ''Ehuzu'' during the [[Politics of Benin|transition to democracy in Benin]].<ref name="Campbell1998">{{cite book|author=Campbell, W. Joseph|title=The Emergent Independent Press in Benin and Côte D'Ivoire: From Voice of the State to Advocate of Democracy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pAjZu5xA93kC&pg=PA5|year=1998|publisher=Praeger|location=Westport|isbn=978-0-275-96309-5|page=5}}</ref>

